headline: 3 High-Yield Utility Stocks to Buy to Create Years of Passive Income
summary: Black Hills is small and boring, but it has a monster 55 year long dividend streak and a 4.4% yield.  Dominion offers a high dividend yield today and growth potential in the future.  Duke Energy operates in regions with strong growth potential.
